# Brewfile - macOS GUI applications via Homebrew
#
# This file is used by `brew bundle` to install macOS casks (GUI apps).
# Uncomment the apps you want to install, then run:
#   brew bundle --file=~/dotfiles/Brewfile
#
# Or just re-run ./install.sh which handles this automatically on macOS.

